				<td colspan="2"><span>Both stink like rotting, maggot infested road kill after 3 days in the hot Texas sun.
<br />

<br />
Extremes are not good.  Better to be in or near the middle ground.  Hitler was an extremest, as was Saddam and Osama Bin-Ladin, and their ilk.  Do you really want to be counted among such figures?
<br />

<br />
Each of you, if you look closely at what you really believe of your own accord, will find that you have a split between both the right and the left, and that many of the things you believe are closer to the middle.  There are exceptions to this, of course.
<br />

<br />
If only the politicians would get a clue and move away from the far ends and back towards the middle.  The move to the far left and right is not good for our country and it will hurt us in the long run.  Such inane political manuvers(sp) divide us, and we cannot stand strong divided as we are at this point.  We are becoming an extremely ripe target for a lot of nasty things to happen.  Some by our own government.
<br />

<br />
The Patriot act is a horror that reminds me of Stalinist Russia and Hitler's Nazi Germany.  I pray it is soon gone.</span></td>
