h*ll, even the extremists are wishy washy, this group wants to kill all muslims, is against abortion, and wants one national language.  Another group wants to kill all muslims, but supports abortion, and wants a dual language sytem.  A third group wants to hug all muslims, supports eating babies, and wants our language to be French.
