<br />

<br />
Example:
<br />

<br />
The Department of Transportation was going to withhold road funds to any State that did not raise the minimum drinking age from 18 to 21.  IMO, that's bullshit and blackmail.  If you can vote and join the working establishment at 18, you should be given all luxuries therein.  
<br />

<br />
States should retain the power to care for its people, the Federal government should only SUPPLEMENT that care...that is no longer the way it is done.  We pay more in Federal taxes than State taxes...again, that is backwards.  
