				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: Conservatism and Liberalism...<a name="44286"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Jun 4 04 6:34 PM</span></td>
